parameters: 【Guild Old Man】 What can I help you with?
I would like to register as an adventurer
冒険者の登録をしたいのですが

【Guild Old Man】 Please fill out the necessary information on this
form.
Please tell me about your background.
Both of my parents are adventurers
I grew up in a rural area
I am confident in my strengths
If it's about speed, I won't lose
I have been diligent in my studies
If luck is considered a strength, then maybe that
足の速さなら負けない
What made you decide to become an adventurer?
【Guild Old Man】 Have you finished writing?

【Guild Old Man】 ...Hmm? Are you really a newbie? You seem quite
skilled.

【Guild Old Man】 Hmmm, very well. Shall I unlock a few warp gates that
match your abilities?
【Guild Old Man】 It seems fine. We will take care of it here.
【Guild Old Man】 Please wait a moment.
【Guild Old Man】 Here is your adventurer registration certificate.

【Guild Old Man】 With this, you will be able to enter the dungeon, but
please be extremely careful as it is a very dangerous place.

【Guild Old Man】 So! For those who have climbed up, there is something
I would like to ask all of you first.

【Guild Old Man】 The request is to pay a fixed amount of gold to the
guild every \C[10]{5 days}\C[0].
【Guild Old Man】 The duration is \C[10]\{15 days\}\C[0].

【Guild Old Man】 Unfortunately, not all adventurers who visit the town
are well-behaved individuals.

【Guild Old Man】 On the contrary, it's mostly the opposite. Many of
them have a rough temperament and are quick to resort to violence
rather than words.

【Guild Old Man】 We are requesting your cooperation as a contribution
towards the cost of maintaining the town's public safety activities,
in order to prevent such individuals from causing trouble.

【Guild Old Man】 Also, if Yamamoto-san were to collapse inside the
dungeon, we would form a search party and go search for him.

【Guild Old Man】 The members of the search party are recruited in the
form of requests from adventurers, and the cost is used to cover the
rewards given to them.

【Guild Old Man】 If we are unable to collect the money, I'm sorry but
we will have to cancel your registration.
【Guild Old Man】 Thank you for your understanding and cooperation.

【Guild Old Man】 Thank you very much. Well then, please take care of us
from now on. Good luck!

【Guild Old Man】 Oh, by the way, as a token of our appreciation for
joining the guild, we have a small gift for you from the guild.
【Guild Old Man】 We hope you can be of help in exploring the dungeon.

\# Obtained Healing Kit. Obtained Sleep Ball. Obtained Shock Ball.
Obtained 3000G.
\#■ Received a set of adventurer's equipment.
【Guild Old Man】 Take care and good luck on your journey.

【Guild Old Man】 Hello. The dungeon is filled with danger, so please be
careful.

【Guild Old Man】 The requests are posted on that bulletin board over
there.

【Guild Old Man】 If you have something you can take on, please bring it
here.
【Guild Old Man】 Alright, then please take care.
